# Linting

After every change, run, **in this order**:
- `uv run ruff format`
- `uv run ruff check --fix`
- `uv run ty check`

# Running the GUI (dev mode)

Start the GUI in-browser with hot reload:
```
uv run python -m photo_darkroom_manager.gui.gui_app
```

This runs the app at `http://localhost:8090`, with hot reload enabled. You can
use Cursor Browser to open it.

# Commit messages

Always use conventional commits for commit messages: https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/#specification.
